      '<p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://www.business-standard.com/world-news/over-23-million-afghans-in-dire-need-of-humanitarian-aid-in-2024-unama-124050600462_1.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">West-made Crisis</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: According to UNAMA, over 23 million Afghans in dire need of humanitarian aid in 2024</span></p><p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://www.unwomen.org/en/news-stories/feature-story/2023/08/women-in-afghanistan-from-almost-everywhere-to-almost-nowhere" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Need Intervention</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: The situation for women in Afghanistan has immensely worsened since 2021</span></p><p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://thediplomat.com/2019/01/36-things-india-has-done-for-afghanistan/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Historical Help</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: India helped Afghanistan Republic in building infrastructure and democracy</span></p><p><a href="https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/india-coordinating-humanitarian-assistance-in-afghanistan-centre-5201082" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Continued Commitment</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: India continues to coordinate humanitarian assistance in Afghanistan </span></p>',
