      '<p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/sri-lanka-expects-fdi-jump-13-bln-with-india-taking-lead-2023-05-24/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Stepping Up</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: Sri Lanka expects FDI to jump to $1.3 billion with India taking the lead</span></p><p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://thediplomat.com/2023/07/sri-lankan-presidents-visit-to-india-signals-growing-economic-and-energy-ties/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Green Priority</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: Agreements on connectivity, renewable energy and technology were signed during Sri Lankan President Ranil Wickremesinghe\'s visit to India in 2023</span></p><p class="ql-align-justify"><a href="https://ceylonhunt.com/cheriyapani/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Ferry Connect</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: All about Cheriyapani, a passenger ferry service between Sri Lanka and India</span></p>',
