    diveContent:
      '<p><a href="https://nadsadhna.com/indian-music-abroad-by-vibhakar-baxi/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Success Abroad</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: The success of Indian music, both classical and popular, has soared phenomenally on foreign shores. There cannot be a corner of this earth where Indian music is not heard.</span></p><p><a href="https://theprint.in/feature/india-ranks-20th-for-global-music-influence-6th-for-uniqueness-in-study-spanning-30-nations/612200/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Global Music Influence</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: The Global Influential Music Index ranked US, UK, France, Germany &amp; Canada as the top 5 musically influential countries worldwide. India was among the 3 Asian countries to feature in the list.</span></p><p><a href="https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/global-consumption-of-indian-music-soared-2000-in-5-years-on-spotify12/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">2000% Rise</a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">: Global consumption of music from India has jumped by more than 2,000% on its platform in the last five years. In 2023 alone, global consumption of music from India jumped 85%.</span></p>',
