    description: '',
    diveContent:
      '<p><a href="https://edition.cnn.com/europe/live-news/moscow-russia-shooting-03-23-24/index.html#:~:text=A%20Friday%20night%20attack%20at%20Crocus%20City%20Hall%2C,claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20without%20providing%20evidence." rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Moscow Attack</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: A Friday night attack at Crocus City Hall, a popular concert venue complex near Moscow, left more than 130 people killed</span></p><p><a href="https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/because-we-are-big-victims-of-terrorism-jaishankar-indias-strong-position-on-israel-hamas-war-2455397-2023-10-30" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Strong Stance</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">:&nbsp;India takes a strong position on terrorism because its people are "big victims of terrorism," said Indian Foreign Minister Dr Jaishankar</span></p>',
