      '<p><a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/media/entertainment/media/imax-posts-record-india-box-office-earnings-in-2023/articleshow/106967633.cms?from=mdr" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Big Cash</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: Hollywood movies and Foreign investors in Indian cinema space are reporting high earnings&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-64286680" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Regional Rocks</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: The global success of ‘RRR’ signals India’s charm&nbsp;</span></p><p><a href="https://ekalavya.art/various-forms-of-indian-theatre-its-significance/#:~:text=Types%20of%20Indian%20Theatre%3A%201%201%29%20Traditional%20Theatre,Theatre%20Art%20...%204%204%29%20Contemporary%20Theatre%20" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Discover Richness</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: Various forms of Indian theatre</span></p>',
