    datePublished: '',
    description: '',
    diveContent:
      '<p><a href="https://www.foodprocessingindia.gov.in/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Land of Opportunities</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: The FDI equity inflow in the Food Processing Sector for the period of April 2021-March 2022 was USD 709.72</span></p><p><a href="https://www.ibef.org/blogs/an-overview-of-the-indian-food-processing-sector" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Overview</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: Exports of processed food climbed from US$ 8.56 billion in 2020-21 to US$ 10.42 billion in 2021-22.</span></p><p><a href="https://www.investindia.gov.in/sector/food-processing" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Industry Scenario</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: The food processing industry has a share of 12.22% in the employment generated in all Registered Factory sector engaging approximately 2.03 Mn people.</span></p><p><a href="https://www.investindia.gov.in/team-india-blogs/innovations-food-packaging-balancing-convenience-and-sustainability" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;">Sustainability, Innovations, and Packaging</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">: The Indian food and beverage packaging industry, with an annual growth of 14.8%, is projected to reach $86 Bn in 2029.</span></p>',
    editor: '',
    excerpt:
      'Looking at the growing processed food industry of India, opportunities in the innovation and collaborations through the eyes of Australian MP',

    expires: '',
