    excerpt:
      "In a notable diplomatic event, H.E. Dr. Vincent Biruta, the Minister of Foreign Affairs and International Cooperation of the Republic of Rwanda, visited India from December 7-8, 2023. This visit aimed to strengthen bilateral ties and explore collaboration opportunities between the two nations. External Affairs Minister, Dr. S. Jaishankar, engaged in delegation-level talks with Minister Biruta. The discussions covered the entire spectrum of bilateral relations, including regional and international issues, and cooperation in multilateral fora.\n\n\n\nH.E. Dr. Vincent Biruta's visit exemplifies the commitment of both nations to strengthen diplomatic ties. The delegation-level talks reflect the depth and significance of the relationship between India and Rwanda. As the visit concludes, it leaves behind the promise of enhanced cooperation and a brighter future for the diplomatic relations between these two nations.",

